&lt;p&gt;La classe &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;HorizontalCrossword&lt;/code&gt; deve contenere i metodi seguenti:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;public-static-string-reversestring-word&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;public static String reverse(String word)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ritorna la stringa &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;word&lt;/code&gt; &lt;em&gt;rovesciata&lt;/em&gt;, ad esempio per &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&quot;cane&quot;&lt;/code&gt; ritorna &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&quot;enac&quot;&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;public-static-string-getrowasstringchar-table-int-row&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;public static String getRowAsString(char[][] table, int row)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ritorna la stringa ottenuta concatenando tutti i caratteri presenti nella riga &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;row&lt;/code&gt; della matrice &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;table&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;public-static-int-searchinrowschar-table-string-word&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;public static int searchInRows(char[][] table, String word)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

